Title: Designates certain lakes and creeks in Lewis and Oneida counties as inland waterways
Summary: Designates Brantingham Lake, Delta Lake, Hinckley Reservoir, Oriskany Creek and West Canada Creek as inland waterways.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the executive law, in relation to including Brantingham Lake, Delta Lake, Hinckley Reservoir, Oriskany Creek and West Canada Creek in the definition of Inland waterways
